item.title: CVE-2018-14788|2024-08-05T09:38:13.975Z -- fuji%20electric -- alpha5%20smart%20loader
item.description: Fuji Electric Alpha5 Smart Loader Versions 3.7 and prior. A buffer overflow information disclosure vulnerability occurs when parsing certain file types.

item.title: CVE-2018-14794|2024-08-05T09:38:13.984Z -- fuji%20electric -- alpha5%20smart%20loader
item.description: Fuji Electric Alpha5 Smart Loader Versions 3.7 and prior. The device does not perform a check on the length/size of a project file before copying the entire contents of the file to a heap-based buffer.
